snippet.title: Choo-Choo Charles new mission gameplay from Summer Game Fest
snippet.description:
The game is Choo-Choo Charles, and you can wishlist and follow it on Steam:  https://store.steampowered.com/app/1766740/ChooChoo_Charles

Other links:  https://linktr.ee/TwoStarGames

Open world indie horror game choo choo charles (some people still think it's called choo choo train scary charlie or something smh).  It's for pc gaming maybe xbox and playstation someday. spooky top scary games is what it is. yes.  SUmmer game fest day of the devs exclusive new gameplay reveal biggest
